我咁話有錢就去整返對眼啦，屌你老母有得醫神早醫左啦。<br />\n因為咁個人好自卑好灰覺得自己好廢無乜前途。<br />\n拍過次拖，拍左一排覺得自己好廢就唔揾條女等佢飛我，唔好拖住人矖人時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bebcc65dfd6489ce836a7a6e01674d02f10507","tid":95691,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"有無咩興趣？"},{"pid":"103227b710dd3075ba9c8abb82392d42461368cb","tid":95691,"uid":23254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">右眼失明</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">雙眼</span>斜視弱視<br />\n<br />\n即係右眼失明定斜視弱視</blockquote><br />\n右眼睇野會有好大撻黑色遮住<br />\n當佢失明算 根本冇用。<br />\n<br />\n雙眼都有弱視斜視</blockquote><br />\n我右眼都係弱視 睇野主要用左眼<br />\n但係可能由細到大都係咁 我又覺得無咩野"},{"pid":"7545727cee06512e0edb8afd8991bb38d6be9b0a","tid":95691,"uid":720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"攬下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd21db34b8b4878c24df2efb4d4d35ea8567b7d","tid":95691,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攬下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa52fb0a463d9a04d4227c302a161e01954e7723","tid":95691,"uid":70940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"攬攬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知講啲咩希望在明天天生我才必有用之類嘅野真係無用<br />\n不過希望你會搵到自己嘅長處/熱誠 堅強咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好覺得自己係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01dca895d7f689afa1815d363e03bedf7bb5586","tid":95691,"uid":4790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攬攬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hk